reviewText: One of my FAVE movies....a lot of cussing but great laughs from the 80s!
CLASSIC....STILL FUNNY. it arrived within three days in new condition.
Purchased for a friend - love this!

Eddie Murphy truely is comedian whose talent can span time.  His material is relatable and sometimes makes us go "Yeah, that really is true/that way"  His impersonations are wonderful and like his other stand up show Delirious, this one is worth a viewing.

I ordered this when I was overseas so I can't complain out delivery. I needed something that was going to make me laugh so why not get something that will guarantee that?  Eddie is funny and helped during those long deployment days. I would say this was a great buy for me.
